text: Syndon twegen dagas on ægwylcum monðe, swahwætswa on þam dagum ongynð, ne wurð hit næfre geendod.
On Ianuarius, þonne se mona biðIIInihta eald andIIII.
On Februarius, þonne he biðVnihta eald andVII.
On Martius, þonne he biðVInihta eald andVII.
On Aprelis, þonne he biðVnihta eald andVIII.
On Maius, þonne he biðVIIInihta eald andIX.
On Iunius, þonne he biðVnihta eald andXVII.
On Iulius, þonne he biðIIInihta eald andXIII.
On Agustus, þonne he biðVIIInihta eald andXIII.
On September, þonne he biðVnihta eald andIX.
On October, þonne he biðVnihta eald andXV.
On Nouember, þonne he biðVIInihta eald andIX.
On December, þonne he biðIIInihta eald andXII.
And swa hit bið, gyme, seþe wylle.
